Example:

A Function triggers when a file is uploaded to Azure Blob â†’ resizes and saves a thumbnail.

âš™ï¸ 2. Azure Logic Apps

Purpose: Automate workflows with no code/low code visual designer.

Use cases:

Connect apps/services (e.g., Outlook, SharePoint, Salesforce)

Send alerts when a file is updated

Schedule data syncs between systems

Example:

When an email with an attachment arrives â†’ upload file to OneDrive â†’ notify in Teams.

ğŸŒ 3. Azure Event Grid

